{"tid":2259074,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"求教 Win10 閃退","createTime":"2020-10-26T13:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T08:34:33.000Z","uid":382383,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a28c6e3c8cbc82c8f800302970cd0c9893f6463","tid":2259074,"uid":382383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"原先在桌面右click正常，但在檔案管理右click一直load, 然後閃退。<br />\n<br />\n後來跟網上方法，我下載了Shell Extensions，看有甚麼檔案有問題，見網友說可以先disable &rdquo;convert to pdf class&rdquo;,試了過後整個畫面不斷閃屏，我就㩒咗工作管理員出來，把Shell Extensions關了。<br />\n<br />\n現後它問我檔案要archive 嗎，我答了是，然後shell extension沒有回應，現在在沒檔案的桌面不斷閃屏。<br />\n<br />\n應該如何處理，很頭痛，文件都在asus laptop裏面。。。"},{"pid":"267e1ed66e9d13bf99cbbdae29800d541e506bc7","tid":2259074,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"換過個mon"},{"pid":"18249d2438582281c34805005c8c65ab574d6e9b","tid":2259074,"uid":382383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"267e1ed66e9d13bf99cbbdae29800d541e506bc7","tid":2259074,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"換過個mon"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"不是mon 的問題， 應該是系統or軟件不斷reload"},{"pid":"dab1a90bc6d01f2adf01a4e21faff314751d71c1","tid":2259074,"uid":374184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f871cbd5cd0e763d0db824e10d1548ea77f6d6","tid":2259074,"uid":370148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dab1a90bc6d01f2adf01a4e21faff314751d71c1","tid":2259074,"uid":374184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a06b9ecba830a3f0563b88858a2652d60ab9802","tid":2259074,"uid":374184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"